    <S id="S1">
        <FORM>42 Ka ni k'ma ki ina, Assi-kame tna-msing hnyn alei ki na sou-oho, ra ni-ni-tna-mado-ni-an millingigh, ka kavanani-an ka missing ti atta ta ti Christus, ka Tama-Pa kariàng ki ymmud ki næi.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S2">
        <FORM>43 Ka sì æugh ki rouha ki wæ'i, ni-d'marang hynna, ka ni-sah-ka-qua mou-qua tou Galilea.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S3">
        <FORM>44 Ka ni-mæddo gmail ti Je-sus ka äoussi ki louloug-an ta Ta-ma Mattæ'i tou pourough ti A-ma tyn.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S4">
        <FORM>45 Irou ka mou-qua ta teni tou Galilæa ni-pa-hyh tatalagh tyni-æn ta ta'u ka makka Galilea, dou ni-kytt'an nein ta mamang ka na ringei tyn tou Jerusalem tou wæi ki ou-vavatoug-han: kani-lum-mad-appa ta neni tou ou-vava-toug-han.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S5">
        <FORM>46 Anna ta ni-salikogh ta ti Jesus mou-qua tou Kana tou Ga-lilæa, ka ni-pa-ha hala-un tyn ta raloum ki hala ki karæumættæh tou hynna. Ka akoumea hynna ta saat ka talalam ki Meisasou ka siba vau, ka pæi-a-lalam-men ki alak tyn ka pæræh tou Kapernaum.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S6">
        <FORM>47 Teni rou ni-milligh ka lummad-den ti Jesus makka Judea mou-qua tou Galilæa ni-mou-qua tyni-æn ka ni-tmoumi-mi-en tyn tyni-æn kou'ou-rapag-auh</FORM>
    </S>
</TEXT>
